title: Beth Stelling

description:
Dewers! My #HoneyDew this week is Beth Stelling! From as early as six, Beth knew how to get the party started! I’ll just say the party trick was something you needed to hear. We talk about struggles with weight and how it feels when you hear things like, “You’ll never be thin” and “I’ve never slept with a bigger girl”. Beth is tough as nails and shares some crazy stories about growing up with divorced parents and getting caught by the cops in a frat house when she was in 8th grade! And her poor dog...
Subscribe, download & review!
